## API Summary

| Module | Base Route | Key Operations |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Auth** | `/api/auth` | `/register`, `/login`, `/profile` |
| **Products** | `/api/products` | `/`, `/:slug`, `/featured` |
| **Categories** | `/api/categories` | `/` |
| **Cart** | `/api/cart` | `/add`, `/update`, `/:cartId` |
| **Orders** | `/api/orders` | `/place` |
| **History** | `/api/history` | `/`, `/:historyId` (DELETE) |

> [!TIP]
> All product photos are served using the paths currently used in your frontend (`/src/assets/images/...`) for immediate compatibility.
